  "description": "This is perfect summer desert. It’s easy and quick to make, and fresh berries are its main ingredient. It can also be a good option for travel because it doesn’t need many ingredients or tools. It’s the best if you cook in the evening and eat for breakfast the next morning, with some [café de olla](/recipes/cafe-de-olla/).",
